    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it's totally ready to hit the road with a new owner today! It runs super smoothly and is perfect if you\u2019re looking for something reliable that still looks great. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 29800.0,
